{"calories":"880","carbs":100,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"The Test Kitchen loves using corkscrew-shaped \u003ci\u003efusilli\u003c/i\u003e because it scoops creamy sauces into its many spirals—a \u003ci\u003emust\u003c/i\u003e for mac and cheese. Inspired by the success of a past mac and cheese, Chef Michelle is melting Fontina, Gruyère, and Parmesan to create the rich, gooey sauce. For a seasonal veggie twist on the crowd-pleasing dish, she’s folding in caramelized Vidalia onions and sautéed kale, then topping it all with a crispy crust of panko breadcrumbs and even more Parmesan.","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"e597c656e5","fat":37,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/28481/Caramelized_Onion_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Kale___0011___HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/28481/hero_Caramelized_Onion_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Kale___0011___HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/28481/menu_small_Caramelized_Onion_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Kale___0011___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/28481/small_square_Caramelized_Onion_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Kale___0011___HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/28481/medium_square_Caramelized_Onion_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Kale___0011___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/28481/recipe_profile_page_Caramelized_Onion_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Kale___0011___HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/28488/Caramelized_Onion_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Kale___0001___THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/28488/menu_small_Caramelized_Onion_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Kale___0001___THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/28485/Caramelized_Onion_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Kale___0023___MOBILE.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/28504/large_cropped_Caramelized_Onion_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Kale___0011___HERO_B.jpg","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}}],"name":"Three-Cheese Mac and Cheese with Kale and Caramelized Onions","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"35-45","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":39,"public_slug":"caramelized-onion-mac-and-cheese-with-kale","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/16401/recipe_card20170901-4-18ywkvh.pdf","recipe_id":3007,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Three-Cheese Mac and Cheese","subtitle":"with Kale and Caramelized Onions","title":"Three-Cheese Mac and Cheese","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you'll be glad you did!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe onions are caramelized when they're very soft, browning in spots, and taste subtly sweet. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eUsing your hands will warm the butter slightly, so it combines with the flour more easily. This mixture will thicken the cheese sauce in Step 4, making for the perfect mac and cheese! \u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBe sure to keep a careful eye on the milk, whisking constantly after adding butter and flour, to prevent burning.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["10\" large pot","12\" large high-sided pan","baking sheet"],"id":3007,"ingredients":["unsalted butter","panko breadcrumbs","grated Parmesan cheese","dinosaur kale","Vidalia onion","fusilli pasta","flour","milk","shredded Fontina cheese","shredded Gruyère cheese","8\" aluminum tin"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"unsalted butter","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/265/medium_square_butter-test.jpg"},{"name":"panko breadcrumbs","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/21/medium_square_PANKO_BREADCRUMBS_copy.jpg"},{"name":"grated Parmesan cheese","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/22/medium_square_parmesan-cheese-2.jpg"},{"name":"dinosaur kale","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/482/medium_square_DINOSAUR_KALE_1_copy.jpg"},{"name":"Vidalia onion","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/896/medium_square_medium_square_ingredient-11.jpg"},{"name":"fusilli pasta","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1957/medium_square_sfoglini_fusili.jpg"},{"name":"flour","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/285/medium_square_FLOUR_copy.jpg"},{"name":"milk","quantity":"12.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/129/medium_square_coconut-milk.jpg"},{"name":"shredded Fontina cheese","quantity":"3.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/423/medium_square_shredded-cheese-asiago.jpg"},{"name":"shredded Gruyère cheese","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/280/medium_square_dairy-gruyere1.jpg"},{"name":"8\" aluminum tin","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/830/medium_square_square_baking_tin.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":14,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":15,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare Ingredients and Make Topping","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/25169/recipe_card_size_1._Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 450°F. Set \u003cstrong\u003ebutter\u003c/strong\u003e aside to soften at room temperature. Bring a large pot of water to a boil over high heat. In a small bowl, stir together \u003cstrong\u003ebreadcrumbs\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003e1 teaspoon olive oil \u003c/strong\u003eto combine. Set breadcrumb topping aside until Step 5. Rinse \u003cstrong\u003ekale \u003c/strong\u003eand trim and discard long stems, then thinly slice leaves crosswise. Peel \u003cstrong\u003eonion\u003c/strong\u003e, halve, and thinly slice.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook Vegetables","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/25170/recipe_card_size_2._Cook_Vegetables.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eHeat \u003cstrong\u003e2 packets butter\u003c/strong\u003e in a large high-sided pan over medium-high heat. When butter is foamy, add \u003cstrong\u003eonion\u003c/strong\u003e and cook, stirring frequently, until brown and softened, 8-10 minutes (see Recipe Tip). Add \u003cstrong\u003ekale\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until beginning to soften, 1-2 minutes more. Season with \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Transfer \u003cstrong\u003evegetables\u003c/strong\u003e to aluminum tin, reshaping if bent (this way, you won't have to wash a plate). Reserve pan for Step 4.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook Fusilli","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/25171/recipe_card_size_3._Cook_Pasta.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eSeason pot of boiling water generously with \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e and stir in \u003cstrong\u003efusilli\u003c/strong\u003e. Cook until very al dente, about 7 minutes, then drain and set aside (your pasta will finish cooking in the oven!). Meanwhile, in a small bowl, combine \u003cstrong\u003eflour\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eremaining\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ebutter \u003c/strong\u003eand, using your fingers, knead together until fully blended to form a smooth paste (see Recipe Tip). Set aside.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Make Cheese Sauce","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/25172/recipe_card_size_4._Make_Sauce.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile fusilli cooks, place\u003cstrong\u003e milk\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.5 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired in pan from vegetables over medium-high heat. Cook, whisking, until milk comes to a boil. Once boiling, whisk in\u003cstrong\u003e flour-butter mixture \u003c/strong\u003euntil smooth and fully dissolved, 30 seconds (see Recipe Tip). Reduce heat to medium and whisk occasionally until sauce is thickened, 2 minutes more. Remove from heat and whisk in\u003cstrong\u003e Fontina\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eGruyère\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003eremaining Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Assemble and Bake Mac and Cheese","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/25173/recipe_card_size_5._Aseemble_and_Bake_2X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eAdd \u003cstrong\u003evegetables \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003ecooked\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003efusilli\u003c/strong\u003e to pan with cheese sauce and gently stir to fully coat. Pour \u003cstrong\u003emac and cheese \u003c/strong\u003einto aluminum tin, evenly sprinkle over \u003cstrong\u003ebreadcrumb topping\u003c/strong\u003e, and place on a baking sheet. Bake until topping is golden brown, 5-7 minutes.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate Mac and Cheese","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/25174/recipe_card_size_6._Plate.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eDivide\u003cstrong\u003e three-cheese mac and cheese with kale and caramelized onions\u003c/strong\u003e between serving plates. Enjoy with fellow cheese lovers!\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"quick prep","slug":"quick-prep","hex_color":null}],"allergens":[{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{"name":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Pasta","slug":"pasta","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"quick prep","slug":"quick-prep","hex_color":null}],"feature":[]}}